                        <interp inst="t18410705-1935-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 21.—
<rs id="t18410705-1935-punishment-116" type="punishmentDescription">
